    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1892-09-12T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1892-09-12T00:00:00-05:00" n="523"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d523">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Adee</persName> to Señor <persName
                            type="to">Bolet Peraza</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1892-09-12">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 12, 1892</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Confirm telegram Saturday. Necessary you at once make complaint and furnish
                    proofs. Confer with district attorney in New York. Judicial proceedings must be
                    instituted by you or some person qualified to complain under oath of facts
                    within personal knowledge.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Alvey A. Adee</hi>,<lb/>
                        <hi rend="italic">Acting Secretary.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
